description: Powers of Ten Science Documentary hosted by Philip Morrison, published by IBM in 1977 - English narration [img]https://docuwiki.net/images/0/07/Powers-of-Ten-Cover.jpg[/img] Information ------------------------------ A scientific film essay, narrated by Phil Morrison. A set of pictures of two picnickers in a park, with the area of each frame one-tenth the size of the one before. Starting from a view of the entire known universe, the camera gradually zooms in until we are viewing the subatomic particles on a man's hand.
